content: Hi! Thank you for contacting XYZ Home Services. May I have your name, please?
Thanks, Kelsey! Could you please provide your address so we can check availability for a plumbing appointment?
I don't want to give my address yet. Just tell me if you have something available this week.
I understand, Kelsey. I do need your address to check our service area and find available appointment slots. Can you provide it now, or even just your zip code?
Why do you need my whole address before I know if you even have spots open? I just want to know if you're booked up or not.

I understand your concern. We ask for your address to ensure you’re within our service area and to verify our availability for plumbing services at your location. Unfortunately, I cannot check for open slots without at least a zip code. Would you be willing to share that?
No, sorry. Forget it. I’ll try someone else.
